---
title: Greek Inspired Bulgur and Chickpea jumble with Feta and Courgette Ribbons
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Bulgur & Chickpea jumble with Feta in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/greek-inspired-bulgur-and-chickpea-jumble-24efb6f1-c0da713c.jpg
